observations.recommendation:
1.18. 	We recommended and Management agreed to:
Reassess the composition of the Inventory and Disposal Committee in consideration of the regular duties and responsibilities, as well as their commitment to their additional duties and responsibilities as Committee members;
Direct the Inventory and Disposal Committee to ensure that the complete physical count of PPEs be done within three months or less in accordance with the provisions of COA Circular No. 2020-006 dated January 31, 2020;
Direct the Inventory and Disposal Committee to take proper action on government properties that are for disposal to prevent their continued deterioration and decline in value leading to loss of possible income from disposal.
